Author: WinonaQuimby
Text: 🍜🤮🍪🍪🍫🍦🤮😫😒⏲️  That's my best attempt at your night in emojis. No brownie so I subbed a chocolate bar. Hope this is an acceptable swap. I def fancied things up with the ramen instead of cup of noodles.  I wish you a night of good sleep. Maybe you won't feel the need to fast tomorrow, at least not a full 24 hours.
